{"tid":1340364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警黑合作 天下無敵","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:58:57.000Z","uid":35547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a44eb26b8c73b0488b0382d3b050169e99eb98d","tid":1340364,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"對住和平示威者就全副gear擺定個陣主動進攻<br />\n百幾個黑社會打人打到上月台打到d人爆曬缸 <br />\n由班黑社會聚集到打完人散去 相信最少都有幾十分鍾<br />\n警察就慢條斯理等黑社會走曬先到場 黎到仲要只係帶住d普通裝備<br />\n真係好撚黑暗 我地仲點鬥 想搵合法途徑制裁班仆街都已經唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚慶係除左兄弟手足 就連女人都比人打到爆缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢件事完全係有預謀有計劃 趁我地大部分人仲係上環果邊就係元朗搞事<br />\n最後我仲要屌埋港鐵老母 個車站完全冇職員控制? 唔撚報警 <br />\n架車係月台死都唔撚開車仲話暫停服務叫人落車 果刻真係困獸鬥送班普通市民去死"},{"pid":"03662502744da933fd524ac2b13f593229ae3367","tid":1340364,"uid":56702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o86UhON.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo86UhON.gif&h=b6ae8a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死黑警對白衫暴徒視而不見 掉頭走！"},{"pid":"b559a0f73eea8ae81e856cf2829f4a9499414b8d","tid":1340364,"uid":172796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XwQAAL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XwQAAL.gif&h=13b01869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dcb8a8c92664dba5d77bf8bf7925def0314ab39","tid":1340364,"uid":172796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9sZCfAO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9sZCfAO.png&h=56d669c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk8b4t9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk8b4t9.png&h=64416b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/